metadata.name: Buddha
metadata.description:
"Drop by drop is the water pot filled. Likewise, the wise man, gathering it little by little, fills himself with good." says Buddha. 

Voxel art by https://twitter.com/voxelqueen & https://twitter.com/nftsfromb_

All collectors can DM us if .obj or .vox file is required. You can put all UtoBits as statues on your Sandbox, Decentraland, CryptoVoxels, Webaverse plots.
